\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6835765 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 You are married, your wife is still living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7481375 SW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6835765 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 What year were you married?
