Yes, yes, we were just taught the certain way that - because you can see - some people do it funnily sort of but we had that one way and always used it all the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6835765 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 What about the way you sat at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7481375 SW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 No, I - I should think I can't just say we'd always dart for our own place you know, but - you know and - mm.
\par 
