\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6835765 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 If you had any worries could you share them with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7481375 SW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 Yes, definitely, yes, indeed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6835765 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 What about with your father?
