re - a bit scared of him you see, you wouldn't - unless it was serious, like if you'd got a bit - involved you see, you'd have to tell him you see but - you - you could keep out of it you wouldn't, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6835765 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
