religious - like he was - he was not against religion and he was - to be there, he'd been brought up himself you could tell but he never bothered with himself but he saw that we did you see, kept us to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6835765 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in certain ways?
