Oh yes, yes, yes, mm - you know, if they were cheeky to the elders they'd - we'd get told off you see, like they'd say you know, got told off, weren't let to go as we liked to. 'Cos we're the youngest we weren't sort of pampered that way, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6835765 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 Did they say that you should hit back or not if another child hurt you?
