\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6835765 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 Did your parents say you should hit back or not if another child hurt you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7481375 SW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 Yes, but - say stick up f
or yourself buy don't go into bother you see but naturally we can't stop you - if somebody comes at you not - retaliating, but they always taught us to - stick up for ourselves you see but - they didn't want us to go into any bother, don't you start any t
rouble at all because you'd - you'd get it from them and get it from em when you come home if you do. Ah, so -
