ung - it used to make me creep, I didn't like to hear them say 'em you see, and he wouldn't swear much other than but - they both used those words you see, it's funny isn't it. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 
