Well it just depends on how the conversation was running like but - if there were any talking going on and you chipped in like - as you - you got - you got - a - a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775953\charrsid7673570 real}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
