\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7481375 SW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 Well it
 was the worst punishment to me - we used to do it - used to send us to bed you see. And I'd rather have had a - a whipping and get to go out again but - we were sent to bed and - when you - after - summer it was after tea early you see, get sent to bed. 
Y
ou done anything wrong, mother told when you came home you see - Sam's been doing so and so, and it's - off you get to bed. And hear - you could hear them running about outside you know - it was double punishment, I would bear a whipping - but to get sent
 to bed and - and - lying in bed, a youngster you know, listen to your - pals outside - screaming and shouting and running around.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6835765 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 Did your mother ever punish you herself or was it all left to your father?
