emember as a child - you know, coming down the passage and - and there's - one or two special fellows always used to make a fuss of you in the public house, and - they'd - the piano in there you see and - I think that's where the - me eldest sister used t
o
 play a bit you see on a - on - but - never went in for it in a big way, but like it was always - a family thing was a piano in those days like you know you thought you were well away if you had a piano. Any - it seems to be - they used the instrument to 
