nless she - you know, she was about near - you asked to go you see, you wont - she'd take you if you said - can I come with you, you know, if she was going out for stores you see you know. Of course she - you see, with - in - she'd buy a lot of things - f
lour and - sugar and - in bulk you see in a public house used to, she'd - she'd have it - oh yes.
