 - there was - one noticeable - was one - the motor wagonettes came out at first - you know they - they'd hold about eight. And see that'd be about 1911 I think when they came out. I know I'd been - and my - my - the - mother's - sister in-law came over a
nd they - they were going out and I - I got - I was - about fourteen, I was going to work at the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10775953\charrsid7673570 mill}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 
