 you see. Well I mean I think my sister was about - I - you know, sulked and all sorts, why can't I go. You know, all this - of course I had a full eight hours to work, I'd work two and I was only fourteen - thirteen, I'd be thirteen. So the - they let me
 
go you see, so that was a happy do you know, going on a trip like that, one of the first motor wagonettes then of course. Anyhow - and first - funny, I got back to the mill next day, and I got - he says, where were you, and he'd only - he was a - an offcu
