at, I went straight round into mill yard and there was two or three firms in it, and - I got a job with a shilling a week better off you see, I - I got - it was about - eleven shillings there and I had ten shillings where I worked for a full week. And - d
id me a good turn. And it was a nicer place to work at.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6835765 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
