 - we - we were happy like just on the sands you see or in the fair, bit of fair grounds you see and they'd leave us and be back - they'd say now see, be here at certain time and we - you know, we'd go playing on our own, oh I was just thinking mostly my 
-
 me elder brother did come, he - he's dead now, he's four and a half years older than me but - usually me sister and I were - sort of together you see and - and the elder brother sometimes but - we - we'd all play about, then arrange to meet them afterwar
