s to - they might have gone in for a drink you see to a public house you see. And then we'd meet and - have a bit of something to eat you see later on you see. So long as - we were happy and - they - they were - contented you see, they could go - let - le
ave us you see. Of course things weren't as busy in those days as they are now because it wasn't everybody that got to go to the seaside you know like it is now. No, we was fortunate because - there were children never saw the seaside not at all.
