\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7481375 SW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10899911\charrsid7673570 Wife, yes, mm. But they all di
